<div class="max-w-3xl">
  <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Bem-vindo, <%= current_user.name %> 👋</h1>
  <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
    Conta ativa: <span class="font-semibold"><%= current_account&.name %></span>
  </p>

  <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6">
    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Life</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
      Esqueleto multi-tenant: autenticação (e-mail/senha + Google), roles
      (<code>admin</code> / <code>super_admin</code>), painel
      <%= link_to "/admin", admin_root_path, class: "text-indigo-600 hover:underline" %>
      e <%= link_to "/super_admin", "/super_admin", class: "text-indigo-600 hover:underline" %>
      (ActiveAdmin). Substitua esta tela e adicione o domínio do seu projeto.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
